responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6773D5C14A079979757F1A9E8832C38D", "I need feet on the ground out there - are the goblins on the move, or have the highwaymen set up shop? I need someone kicking the rubbish heaps and poking the bone-piles, chasing down rat-holes and busting the dust! Most importantly though? I need those way-markers lit!")
